      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice the <strong>aubergines</strong> in half and then into strips</p><p>Peel and slice the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>into wedges</p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the<strong> garlic</strong></p>",
